Sudan, Zaire, Uganda, Kenya, Tanzania, Zambia, Malawi, Mozambique, Zimbabwe, Botswana, South Africa and Madagascar (Fig. 548). Confusion in the determination of species frequent. Accordingly only verified records are mapped. Additional country records, not verified, are Ivory Coast and Mali (
Omer-Cooper 1965
) and Senegal (
Legros 1972
).
